I forgot about my chips so I got up and stubbed my toe by my small wooden table. I later got bored of watching YouTube so then I went to the living room to watch T.V and found my uncle filled the air in the living room with smokes from cigarettes. I went back to my room and found my cousin being very loud playing fortnite again. My other cousin that was 12 years old was eating a cake while scratching a fork on his plate. I went outside the house to get some calm peace then I was stopped my a wasp. I went back inside and and hoping that YouTube won't crash again so I open it up. I watched a video about science since I'm interested in it then got an ad about the Logan Brothers crying like babies. The ad was almost 3 minutes long. I then gave up on YouTube and went to get toilet paper to dry my tears since my day has been miserable, but then I ran out of toilet paper.
